    },
    {
      "Text": "親レコードの詳細画面に明細リスト (子レコード群) をインライン表示・編集するField。",
      "Icon": "",
      "Style": "Default",
      "RelativeField": "",
      "OnClick": "",
      "Name": "P_0_0",
      "IgnoreModification": false,
      "OnValidateInput": "",
      "TypeFullName": "Codeer.LowCode.Blazor.Repository.Design.LabelFieldDesign"
    },
    {
      "Text": "受注ヘッダ + 受注明細、見積 + 見積行 など 1:N 親子関係でよく使う。",
      "Icon": "",
      "Style": "Default",
      "RelativeField": "",
      "OnClick": "",
      "Name": "P_0_1",
      "IgnoreModification": false,
      "OnValidateInput": "",
      "TypeFullName": "Codeer.LowCode.Blazor.Repository.Design.LabelFieldDesign"
    },
    {
      "Text": "ListField との違い",
      "Icon": "",
      "Style": "H5",
      "RelativeField": "",
      "OnClick": "",
      "Name": "H_1",
      "IgnoreModification": false,
      "OnValidateInput": "",
      "TypeFullName": "Codeer.LowCode.Blazor.Repository.Design.LabelFieldDesign"
    },
    {
      "Text": "DetailListField は親の Submit と同時に子の挿入/更新/削除も一括コミットされる。",
      "Icon": "",
      "Style": "Default",
      "RelativeField": "",
      "OnClick": "",
      "Name": "P_1_0",
      "IgnoreModification": false,
      "OnValidateInput": "",
      "TypeFullName": "Codeer.LowCode.Blazor.Repository.Design.LabelFieldDesign"
    },
    {
      "Text": "ListField は独立した一覧 (検索結果、別レコードへのリンク先)。",
      "Icon": "",
      "Style": "Default",
      "RelativeField": "",
      "OnClick": "",
      "Name": "P_1_1",
      "IgnoreModification": false,
      "OnValidateInput": "",
      "TypeFullName": "Codeer.LowCode.Blazor.Repository.Design.LabelFieldDesign"
    },
    {
      "Text": "DetailListField の各行は親 Module の状態と同じ Submit 単位 (＝同一トランザクション)。",
      "Icon": "",
      "Style": "Default",
      "RelativeField": "",
      "OnClick": "",
      "Name": "P_1_2",
      "IgnoreModification": false,
      "OnValidateInput": "",
      "TypeFullName": "Codeer.LowCode.Blazor.Repository.Design.LabelFieldDesign"
    },
    {
      "Text": "親子削除 (DeleteTogether)",
      "Icon": "",
      "Style": "H5",
      "RelativeField": "",
      "OnClick": "",
      "Name": "H_2",
      "IgnoreModification": false,
      "OnValidateInput": "",
      "TypeFullName": "Codeer.LowCode.Blazor.Repository.Design.LabelFieldDesign"
    },
    {
      "Text": "DeleteTogether=true で親削除時に子レコードも削除される (デフォルト true)。",
      "Icon": "",
      "Style": "Default",
      "RelativeField": "",
      "OnClick": "",
      "Name": "P_2_0",
      "IgnoreModification": false,
      "OnValidateInput": "",
      "TypeFullName": "Codeer.LowCode.Blazor.Repository.Design.LabelFieldDesign"
    },
    {
      "Text": "親子関係 (SearchCondition)",
      "Icon": "",
      "Style": "H5",
      "RelativeField": "",
      "OnClick": "",
      "Name": "H_3",
      "IgnoreModification": false,
      "OnValidateInput": "",
      "TypeFullName": "Codeer.LowCode.Blazor.Repository.Design.LabelFieldDesign"
    },
    {
      "Text": "親PK = 子FK を FieldVariableMatchCondition で記述する。",
      "Icon": "",
      "Style": "Default",
      "RelativeField": "",
      "OnClick": "",
      "Name": "P_3_0",
      "IgnoreModification": false,
      "OnValidateInput": "",
      "TypeFullName": "Codeer.LowCode.Blazor.Repository.Design.LabelFieldDesign"
    },
    {
      "Text": "親の新規作成時、子は親PKがまだ無いのでテンポラリIDで管理される (フレームワーク内部処理)。",
      "Icon": "",
      "Style": "Default",
      "RelativeField": "",
      "OnClick": "",
      "Name": "P_3_1",
      "IgnoreModification": false,
